instigate Princess Anyang!

42
00:03:32,930 --> 00:03:33,970
Take them out!

43
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:36,880
Cut out their tongues!

44
00:03:37,010 --> 00:03:37,720
Yes, Your Majesty.

45
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:39,430
I was wrong, Your Majesty.

46
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:40,880
Your Highness, please save us!

47
00:03:40,900 --> 00:03:41,980
Your Highness!

48
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,450
Your Majesty, spare our lives!

49
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,650
I was wrong, Your Majesty!

50
00:03:44,670 --> 00:03:45,300
Your Majesty!

51
00:03:45,329 --> 00:03:46,130
Your Highness!

52
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,230
Save me!

53
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:48,520
Don't you forget

54
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,740
it was my father who helped you return to the capital.

55
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:52,570
Are you trying to bite the hand that feeds you?

56
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:54,700
I will definitely keep my promise to you

57
00:03:54,730 --> 00:03:55,930
and the King of Nanjiang.

58
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,840
I'm keeping her alive

59
00:03:58,260 --> 00:04:00,060
only to torment her.

60
00:04:00,730 --> 00:04:02,260
I need you to stay alive.

61
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:03,560
Before I find out

62
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,560
what Lord Ji did to you back then

63
00:04:04,690 --> 00:04:10,260
♫A thousand sails have passed, spanning the ages♫

64
00:04:05,700 --> 00:04:07,530
and what you're still hiding,

65
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:10,220
nothing can happen to you.

66
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:17,060
♫The lone swan cries out in sorrow♫

67
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:17,760
How is she?

68
00:04:17,910 --> 00:04:19,640
Lady Pei has been overthinking,

69
00:04:19,670 --> 00:04:20,870
causing her physically weak.

70
00:04:20,899 --> 00:04:21,470
She's weak

71
00:04:21,490 --> 00:04:22,460
