72
00:04:22,650 --> 00:04:25,330
If we don't use the hot springs of Mount Yuhuang to nourish her,

73
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:28,100
she might have a high fever in the next few days.

74
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,420
How could she use the royal hot springs?

75
00:04:31,250 --> 00:04:33,340
I'll take my leave.

76
00:04:35,909 --> 00:04:36,710
Master.

77
00:04:40,530 --> 00:04:42,090
You're really working hard.

78
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:44,409
This memorial has turned upside down.

79
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,730
Father,

80
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:48,700
