81
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,810
When will Su Wuyang issue the decree

82
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:51,990
[King of Nanjiang]

83
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,330
to officially make you the Empress?

84
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:53,960
I'm not quite sure.

85
00:04:53,990 --> 00:04:54,990
It should be soon.

86
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:01,050
Idiot.

87
00:05:01,260 --> 00:05:03,860
Why can't you even get into Su Wuyang's bed?

88
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:08,480
I don't care what methods you use.

89
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:11,010
Become the Empress as soon as possible,

90
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,710
and conceive a royal heir.

91
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:19,200
So that when it comes to the worst,

92
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,280
I can find a way to eliminate Su Wuyang

93
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:23,420
and ascend the throne with his son.

94
00:05:29,050 --> 00:05:30,030
Your Highness,

95
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,450
are you alright?

96
00:05:34,250 --> 00:05:36,070
Father doesn't even bother

97
00:05:36,590 --> 00:05:39,030
