114
00:06:30,650 --> 00:06:32,640
Your Majesty, please be merciful with your words.

115
00:06:31,050 --> 00:06:32,890
♫Slips into the world without a trace♫

116
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:38,130
♫Only awakening those who have experienced the story themselves♫

117
00:06:39,110 --> 00:06:40,820
♫You and I in this world♫

118
00:06:39,350 --> 00:06:40,430
What's wrong with you?

119
00:06:42,090 --> 00:06:43,820
♫Just like fleeting mayflies♫

120
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:46,000
Nangong Ying.

121
00:06:44,810 --> 00:06:46,550
♫We loved each other♫

122
00:06:46,030 --> 00:06:47,170
Stop pretending.

123
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,480
Wasn't it you who made me like this?

124
00:06:47,650 --> 00:06:49,620
♫But we were parted by fate♫

125
00:06:50,409 --> 00:06:52,909
If Your Majesty insist on believing I did it,

126
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:51,590
