132
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,920
♫You and I are just♫

133
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:05,480
Nangong Ying.

134
00:07:05,090 --> 00:07:06,660
♫Travelers in this world, with no time for sorrow or joy♫

135
00:07:06,740 --> 00:07:08,340
Remember this:

136
00:07:07,620 --> 00:07:12,390
